'''Tikal''' (or Tik'al, according to the more current orthography) is one of the largest of the ancient cities of the [[Wikipedia:Maya civilization|Maya civilization]]. It is located in Petén department of [[Wikipedia:Guatemala|Guatemala]]. The site is part of Guatemala's Tikal National Park and in 1979 it was declared a [[Wikipedia:UNESCO|UNESCO]] [[Wikipedia:World Heritage Site|World Heritage Site]]. It was used as a filming location for [[Yavin 4]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

The shot where a Rebel oversees the [[Millennium Falcon]] landing on Yavin was taken on top of a building known as Temple IV looking east where Temples I, II and III can be seen on film.

